            <p>
                Climate change means changes in weather patterns over time. In Kenya, we are seeing more droughts and floods. This affects farmers and all of us.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="effects" class="card">
            <h2>Effects in Kenya</h2>
            <p>
                Farmers struggle when rains fail. Food prices go up. Sometimes, heavy rains destroy roads and homes. Wildlife also suffers when water sources dry up.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="solutions" class="card">
